         <div type="translation">
            <ab>O. OIM 19154, recto: (1) Year 28, third month of shemw, day 26.  The donkey was given (2) to Patwtw for (3) its bakw, that is 1/4 [oipe?] per day.  O. OIM 19154, verso: (1) Year 28, fourth month of shemw, day 23.  (2) The donkey was brought (3) up.</ab>
